  "description": "A bright blue sky serves as the backdrop for three birds in flight. The bird at the top is larger and more prominently displayed, with a white body and dark wingtips, appearing to be a gull. Its beak is yellow and open, suggesting it might be calling out. The two birds below are smaller and darker, silhouetted against the bright sky, making it difficult to identify their species, but they appear to be shorebirds. The image captures a sense of freedom and movement.",
